        <Parent_String>self-loading [300227074], operational attributes for firearms [300227788], operational attributes [300191763], attributes and properties by specific type [300226808], Attributes and Properties (hierarchy name) [300123559], Physical Attributes Facet [300264087]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
